Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.18,0:00:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what a gorgeous day!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.53,0:00:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash must have gotten up early\Nfor once and cleared all the clouds away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet all of Ponyville is gonna be out,\Nenjoying the sunshine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Where is everypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it some sort of pony holiday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Does my breath stink?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not more than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...zombies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... not very likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not likely but possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Psst!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.80,0:00:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.67,0:00:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come 'ere!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Before she gets you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?! The zombie pony?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.90,0:00:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Zzzombie pony?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, there are no zombie ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.02,0:01:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, what are you doing\Nhere alone in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not alone in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.57,0:01:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, what are you all\Ndoing here in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.44,0:01:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're h-hidin' from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see her, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see Zecora?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom! I told you never to say that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I saw here glance this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Glance eeevilly this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...and then a bunch of you\Nflip out for no good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No good reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You call protectin' your kin no good reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, as soon as my sister saw Zecora ridin' into town...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...she started shakin' in her lil' horse shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Diiid nooot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So I swept her up and brought her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked here myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,For safekeepin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack! I'm not a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not from that creepy Zecora.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's mysterious...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinister...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And spoooky!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you cut that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:03:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at those stripes. So garish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a zebra.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A zebra. And her stripes aren't\Na fashion choice, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They're what she was born with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Born where? I've never seen\Na pony like that in these parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,'cept her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she's probably not from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's not a pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My books say that zebras come from a faraway land.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've never seen her in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does she live?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She lives in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Everfree Forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Everfree Forest just ain't natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The plants grow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Animals care for themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the clouds move...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...ALL ON THEIR OWN!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And that wicked enchantress Zecora\Nlives there, doing her evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's so evil I even wrote a song about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:04:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's an evil enchantress!\NShe does evil dances!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And if you look deep in her eyes\NShe puts you in trances!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then what will she do?\NShe'll mix up an evil brew!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then she'll gobble you up\NIn a big tasty stew!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So... WATCH OUT!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.67,0:04:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. Catchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.26,0:04:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a work in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all just a lot of gossip and rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now tell me, what exactly have you\Nactually seen Zecora do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Once a month she comes into Ponyville...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she lurks by the stores...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she digs at the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good gracious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But how is any of this bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she comes to town to visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Maybe she's just tryin' to be neighborly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe she's not lurking by the stores,\Nmaybe she's going to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...lurk-free, to so some shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Everypony likes to shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I think...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom! Hush and let the big ponies talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a big pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what about digging at the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta admit that's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What if she's digging for innocent creatures?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sure there's an explanation\Nfor everything Zecora does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And if anypony here were actually\Nbrave enough to approach her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...she would find out the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm brave enough.\NI'm gonna find out myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You ponies are being ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I heard that Zecora...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...EATS HAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, I eat hay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You eat hay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I heard it's\Nthe eeevil way she eats hay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where's Apple Bloom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:05:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The door's open!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She went outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And Zecora is still out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That silly lil' filly...\NI told her to stay put!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, you stay here in case\NApple Bloom comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You get back here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Beware! Beware, you ponyfolk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Those leaves of blue are not a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You keep your crazy mumbo-jumbo\Nto yourself, ya hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Beware! Beware!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Back at you, Zecora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You and your lame curse\Nare the ones who better beware.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why couldn't you just listen to your big sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what kind of nasty curse\NZecora could have just put on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like in my song!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Evil enchantress! With the dances!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the trances!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys, there's no such thing as curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's interesting to hear\Ncoming from from Miss Magic Pants herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My magic, real magic comes from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the skill you're born with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses are artificial. Fake magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cantrip with potions and incantations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All smoke and mirrors meant to scare.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But curses have no real power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just an old pony tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna learn that some pony tales...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...really are true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's an evil enchantress!\NShe does evil dances!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,BEWAAARE! BEWAAARE!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you look deep in her eyes\NShe will put you in trances!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, was that supposed to scare us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wicked, wicked zebra!\N-A curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then what will she do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Some pony tales really are true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then she'll gobble you up\NIn a big tasty stew!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooo... WATCH OUT!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... What a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses-shmurses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Zecora cursed my hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Or she cursed my horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,None of these books have a cure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be a real reason for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,An illness? An allergy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:08:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I said a real reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that points to something real.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"Supernaturals"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, the word "supernatural" refers to\Nthings like ghosts and spirits and zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Which are as make believe as curses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This book is just a bunch of hooey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if you're wrong, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What if this really is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"A purse"? How could it be a purse?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Say it, don't spray it, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She's... trying to say... ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...Zecora... ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...she zapped us all with a... ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.46,0:09:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I have to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to say I told you so, Twilight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I told you so!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a curse, I tells you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:09:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But Fluttershy seems just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. There doesn't seem to be\Na thing wrong with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you care to tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So... you're not gonna tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're not or yes, you will?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good gravy, girl! What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all of you. We got...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hairity...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Crash...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Spitty Pie...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Appletini...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Flutterguy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I got nuthin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle. I mean, seriously,\NI can't even work with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no joke, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now start looking for more\Nbooks so I can find a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we'll find a cure\Nfor this curse at Zecora's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go to Zecora's and force her\Nto remove this hex.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a hex either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't followed Zecora in the first place,\Nnone of this would have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I just gotta fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now where does she think she's goin' this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what you say, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to pony up and confront Zecora.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, girls! Are you with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And I as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I don't know. Seems awfully dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you, Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[She's gone!]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Has somepony stepped on her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Or sat on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity's hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh! Pinkie, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Really... Ah! Ever heard of personal space?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[Nope!]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom is gone too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet they went after Zecora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we better go find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, girls. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Oh dear, ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is so unseemly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! A little help here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oopsie. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta stay here and look for the cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight Flopple!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn around right now, missy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No?! You can't ignore direct order\Nfrom your big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Applejack. But *I'm* the big sister now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom! You come back here\Nright this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna tell Big Macintosh on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, pony feathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, girls. We've got to get to Zecora's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Easier said than done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Heeey! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow! Thank Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get to Zecora's pronto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it up, pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,YEEHAW!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Rainbow Dash! Other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I look horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[No. This looks horrible.]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my. That place really does look horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice decorations. If you like creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"She stole your song?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Pinkie. Doesn't sound anything like your song.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's an evil enchantress\NAnd she does evil dances{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And if you look deep in her eyes\NShe will put you in trances{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then what will she do?\NShe'll mix up an evil brew{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And she'll gobble you up\NIn a big tasty stew{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So... watch out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw those terrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you believe us, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary looking masks, confusing incantations\Nand a great, big, bubbling cauldron?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Everything is pointing to Zecora being...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What if Zecora is just making soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The perfect temperature for ponies, I presume.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, where is that little Apple Bloom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What if she's making Apple Bloom soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What if she's making Apple Bloom soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming for ya, Apple Bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Heel, Rainbow Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done with Apple Bloom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies! What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You know not what you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gone and spilled my precious brew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on to you, Zecora.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't wanna believe that you cursed us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...but the evidence is overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You made me look ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You made me sound ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You ruined my horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You destroy my home, destroy my work...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...then rudely accuse me of being a jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You put this curse on us,\Nnow you're gonna uncurse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It is unwise to venture down this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Your actions will make my anger explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Apple Bloom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Zecora! I think I found\Nall the things you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What in Ponyville is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom! You're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Zecora is an evil enchantress, who\Ncursed us and was gonna cook you up in a soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did those silly fillies finally get in your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You know there's no such thing as a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom, sweetie. You can't just\Nstand there and tell me this isn't a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you will remember back,\Nthe words I spoke were quite exact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Beware. Beware, you ponyfolk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Those leaves of blue are not a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a warnin'. About that blue plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called poison joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That plant is much like poison oak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:17:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But its results are like a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the hay does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It means this plant does not breed wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead this plant just wants a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Will somepony please talk normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think what she's saying is that\Nwhen we ran in to save Apple Bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...we ran into the poison joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All our problems are just little jokes it played on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,LITTLE JOKES?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But... what about the cauldron?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And the chanting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And a creepy decor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasures of the native land where I am from.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This one speaks "hello" and this "welcome".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not welcoming at all, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The words I chanted were from olden times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Something you call a nursery rhyme.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But... the cauldron... the Apple Bloom soup...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.95,0:18:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lookie here, Twilight.\NThat pot o' water wasn't for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It was for all these herbal ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The cure for poison joke is\Na simple all-natural remedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You just gotta take a bubble bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But I tried to find a cure in all my books\Nand couldn't find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What book has this "natural remedy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is the book, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sad that you lack it in your library.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I do have this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't look inside,\Nbecause the title was so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"Supernaturals: natural remedies\Nand cure-alls that are simply... super."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Zecora.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the answer the whole time\Nif only I bothered to look inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe next time you will take a second look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And not judge the cover of the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Zecora, would you be kind enough to mix up\Nanother batch of the herbal bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mix it up I certainly will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet I am missing an herb from Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But whenever Zecora comes to town,\Nall the shops are mysteriously closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well... I think we can help you with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Rose! How awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The wicked enchantress has cursed them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The horror! The horror!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisy, we need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Princess Celestia."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"My friends and I all learned\Nan important lesson this week:"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Never judge a book by its cover."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Someone may look unusual or funny or scary..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"...but you have to look past that\Nand learn who they are inside."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Real friends don't care what your cover is."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's the contents of the pony that count."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"And a good friend, like a good book,\Nis something that will last forever."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Your faithful student, Twilight Sparkle."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Zecora, I would love to\Nget the recipe for this bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simply luxurious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack! Hey, where is Applejack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here, lil' sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't tiny no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I have never felt so lovely\Nin all of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh! I never realized\Nhow horrible is not to be able to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean I love talking so much and I couldn't\Ntalk at all when my tongue was all EEEH!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the worst! Don't you agree, Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Synced by Nathan2000\Nhttp://mlp.wikia.com/wiki/User:Nathan2000
